warnings.message: The [median build time](/pipelines/github.com/estafette/estafette-ci-api/statistics?last=25) of this pipeline is **5m35s**. This is far too slow, please optimize your build speed by using smaller images or running less intensive steps to ensure it finishes within 2 minutes.
